erflow-hidden text-center\">Wikipedia</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Al Jazeera</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1.</span></span></span></a><br></span></span><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">AP News &ndash; ONU critica bombardeios em instala&ccedil;&otilde;es da OMS</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.washingtonpost.com/world/2025/07/21/un-facilities-hit-in-gaza/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">The Washington Post.</span></span></span></a><br></span></span><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] bg-[#FCECC1] dark:bg-[#64572A] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">AP News &ndash; 28 pa&iacute;ses pedem fim imediato do conflito</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"instant-open\" aria-describedby=\"radix-&laquo;r5i1&raquo;\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\" aria-describedby=\"radix-&laquo;r5i1&raquo;\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium bg-token-text-primary! text-token-main-surface-primary! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://apnews.com/article/e4062cffa9585790061105236a93d8e5?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between overflow-hidden\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">AP News.&nbsp;</span></span></span></a><br></span></span></span></p>', 'tinymce', '2025-07-22 10:34:01', 1, '687f93592d6bd.jpg', 36, 8, 12, '2025-07-22 10:34:01', '2025-08-17 13:56:18'),
(39, '72% dos brasileiros veem impacto de conflitos mundiais na economia, aponta pesquisa', 'Estudo do Ipsos‑Ipec indica que 72% dos brasileiros acreditam que guerras globais afetam muito a economia nacional; apenas 25% se consideram bem informados.', '72-dos-brasileiros-veem-impacto-de-conflitos-mundiais-na-economia-aponta-pesquisa', '<h3 data-start=\"791\" data-end=\"841\"><img src=\"https://www.brasilhilario.com.br/uploads/images/687faf792db94.jpg?1753198456184\" alt=\"imagem do lula \" width=\"613\" height=\"409\"></h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"791\" data-end=\"841\">Economia nacional sob press&atilde;o internacional.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"843\" data-end=\"1192\">Uma pesquisa recente realizada pelo Instituto Ipsos-Ipec revelou que <strong data-start=\"912\" data-end=\"1006\">72% dos brasileiros acreditam que conflitos globais impactam fortemente a economia do pa&iacute;s</strong>. A sondagem ouviu duas mil pessoas em mais de 130 munic&iacute;pios e foi conduzida entre os dias 3 e 8 de julho de 2025. A margem de erro &eacute; de dois pontos percentuais para mais ou para menos.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1524\">Essa percep&ccedil;&atilde;o da popula&ccedil;&atilde;o reflete uma crescente preocupa&ccedil;&atilde;o com os desdobramentos de guerras, san&ccedil;&otilde;es econ&ocirc;micas e instabilidades pol&iacute;ticas em pa&iacute;ses como Ucr&acirc;nia, R&uacute;ssia, Israel e Ir&atilde; &mdash; eventos que, mesmo ocorrendo fora do territ&oacute;rio nacional, influenciam diretamente os pre&ccedil;os de combust&iacute;veis, alimentos, exporta&ccedil;&otilde;es e c&acirc;mbio.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1194\" data-end=\"1524\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1531\" data-end=\"1576\">Rela&ccedil;&otilde;es diplom&aacute;ticas tamb&eacute;m preocupam.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"1578\" data-end=\"1906\">Al&eacute;m da preocupa&ccedil;&atilde;o econ&ocirc;mica, <strong data-start=\"1609\" data-end=\"1746\">66% dos entrevistados disseram acreditar que as tens&otilde;es internacionais tamb&eacute;m afetam negativamente as rela&ccedil;&otilde;es diplom&aacute;ticas do Brasil</strong>. Esse dado mostra que a popula&ccedil;&atilde;o come&ccedil;a a entender que conflitos n&atilde;o s&atilde;o apenas quest&otilde;es militares ou pol&iacute;ticas externas, mas t&ecirc;m reflexos reais no cotidiano.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1908\" data-end=\"2145\">Em um cen&aacute;rio global onde blocos econ&ocirc;micos se fortalecem e parcerias comerciais se tornam estrat&eacute;gicas, qualquer abalo nas rela&ccedil;&otilde;es internacionais pode gerar instabilidade nos acordos comerciais, investimentos e no acesso a tecnologias.</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2152\" data-end=\"2204\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2152\" data-end=\"2204\">Baixo n&iacute;vel de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o, mas alta percep&ccedil;&atilde;o.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"2206\" data-end=\"2495\">Curiosamente, embora grande parte dos brasileiros reconhe&ccedil;a os efeitos dos conflitos na economia, <strong data-start=\"2304\" data-end=\"2376\">apenas 25% afirmam estar bem informados sobre pol&iacute;tica internacional</strong>. A maioria (46%) se diz &ldquo;mais ou menos informada&rdquo;, e outros 27% admitem ter pouco ou nenhum conhecimento sobre o tema.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2497\" data-end=\"2797\">Esse abismo entre a percep&ccedil;&atilde;o e o n&iacute;vel de informa&ccedil;&atilde;o pode ser reflexo de uma cobertura fragmentada na m&iacute;dia e da dificuldade de acesso a an&aacute;lises aprofundadas sobre pol&iacute;tica externa. Isso tamb&eacute;m abre espa&ccedil;o para desinforma&ccedil;&atilde;o e discursos polarizados sobre o papel do Brasil no cen&aacute;rio internacional.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"2497\" data-end=\"2797\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"2804\" data-end=\"2871\">Imagem dos pa&iacute;ses em conflito: R&uacute;ssia e Ir&atilde; lideram rejei&ccedil;&atilde;o.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"2873\" data-end=\"2994\">O levantamento tamb&eacute;m perguntou aos entrevistados qual a opini&atilde;o deles sobre pa&iacute;ses envolvidos em tens&otilde;es internacionais:</p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"2996\" data-end=\"3479\">\r\n<li data-start=\"2996\" data-end=\"3113\">\r\n<p data-start=\"2998\" data-end=\"3113\"><strong data-start=\"2998\" data-end=\"3014\">R&uacute;ssia e Ir&atilde;</strong> lideram o &iacute;ndice de imagem negativa, com mais de <strong data-start=\"3064\" data-end=\"3112\">70% dos brasileiros com opini&atilde;o desfavor&aacute;vel</strong>.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"3114\" data-end=\"3226\">\r\n<p data-start=\"3116\" data-end=\"3226\"><strong data-start=\"3116\" data-end=\"3138\">Israel e Palestina</strong> tamb&eacute;m dividem opini&otilde;es: enquanto 61% reprovam a Palestina, Israel tem rejei&ccedil;&atilde;o de 52%.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"3227\" data-end=\"3386\">\r\n<p data-start=\"3229\" data-end=\"3386\"><strong data-start=\"3229\" data-end=\"3240\">Ucr&acirc;nia</strong>, embora seja retratada como v&iacute;tima de invas&atilde;o russa, tem apoio limitado: apenas 32% expressaram simpatia, enquanto 53% mant&ecirc;m uma vis&atilde;o negativa.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"3387\" data-end=\"3479\">\r\n<p data-start=\"3389\" data-end=\"3479\">J&aacute; os <strong data-start=\"3395\" data-end=\"3413\">Estados Unidos</strong> dividem o p&uacute;blico: 45% t&ecirc;m opini&atilde;o favor&aacute;vel, e 29% desfavor&aacute;vel.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"3481\" data-end=\"3681\">Esses dados revelam que, embora a maioria n&atilde;o se considere bem informada, os brasileiros est&atilde;o formando impress&otilde;es fortes com base nas informa&ccedil;&otilde;es que recebem, principalmente da m&iacute;dia e redes sociais.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"3481\" data-end=\"3681\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"3688\" data-end=\"3731\">Diferen&ccedil;as por g&ecirc;nero e escolaridade.</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"3733\" data-end=\"4055\">A pesquisa tamb&eacute;m mostrou que <strong data-start=\"3763\" data-end=\"3845\">homens e pessoas com maior escolaridade tendem a se considerar mais informados</strong> sobre pol&iacute;tica internacional e t&ecirc;m opini&otilde;es mais favor&aacute;veis a pa&iacute;ses aliados do Ocidente, como os EUA e a Ucr&acirc;nia. J&aacute; entre os que t&ecirc;m menor escolaridade, &eacute; maior a propor&ccedil;&atilde;o dos que dizem estar desinformados.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"4057\" data-end=\"4238\">Essas divis&otilde;es indicam que o acesso &agrave; informa&ccedil;&atilde;o e o n&iacute;vel educacional influenciam diretamente a vis&atilde;o sobre o cen&aacute;rio global e os julgamentos pol&iacute;ticos e econ&ocirc;micos derivados dele.</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"4245\" data-end=\"4299\">&nbsp;</h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"4245\" data-end=\"4299\">O que os dados revelam sobre o Brasil no mundo?</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"4301\" data-end=\"4562\">O estudo da Ipsos-Ipec refor&ccedil;a que o brasileiro m&eacute;dio n&atilde;o est&aacute; alheio ao que acontece no exterior. Pelo contr&aacute;rio: reconhece que guerras e conflitos n&atilde;o respeitam fronteiras e que o Brasil, mesmo distante geograficamente, sente os impactos por meio da economia.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"4564\" data-end=\"4821\">Esse tipo de percep&ccedil;&atilde;o &eacute; crucial em um mundo cada vez mais globalizado, onde os efeitos de uma guerra na Europa ou no Oriente M&eacute;dio podem chegar ao bolso do cidad&atilde;o por meio do aumento da infla&ccedil;&atilde;o, queda no valor da moeda e mudan&ccedil;a nas pol&iacute;ticas comerciais.</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"4564\" data-end=\"4821\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 data-start=\"5468\" data-end=\"5477\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Fontes</span></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"5481\" data-end=\"5668\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><a class=\"\" href=\"https://www.metropoles.com/brasil/para-72-dos-brasileiros-conflitos-mundiais-afetam-muito-a-economia\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"5481\" data-end=\"5666\">Metr&oacute;poles &ndash; Para 72% dos brasileiros, conflitos mundiais afetam muito a economia</a></span><br><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><a class=\"cursor-pointer\" target=\"_new\" rel=\"noopener\" data-start=\"5671\" data-end=\"5884\">Roma News &ndash; Maioria dos brasileiros acredita que conflitos mundiais afetam economia</a></span></p>', 'tinymce', '2025-07-22 12:32:53', 1, '687fafac7819a.jpg', 51, 7, 12, '2025-07-22 12:32:53', '2025-08-16 00:25:06');
INSERT INTO `posts` (`id`, `titulo`, `resumo`, `slug`, `conteudo`, `editor_type`, `data_publicacao`, `publicado`, `imagem_destacada`, `visualizacoes`, `categoria_id`, `autor_id`, `criado_em`, `atualizado_em`) VALUES
(40, 'Mais de 7.500 exoplanetas já foram descobertos, aponta Nasa', 'Estudo revela que existem cerca de 7.510 planetas fora do Sistema Solar. Saiba como são detectados, quantos estão em zonas habitáveis e o que vem por aí.', 'mais-de-7-500-exoplanetas-ja-foram-descobertos-aponta-nasa', '<h3 data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"273\"><img src=\"https://www.brasilhilario.com.br/uploads/images/687fb3f83ee7d.jpg\" alt=\"imagem dos planetas\" width=\"715\" height=\"402\"></h3>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"247\" data-end=\"273\">O que s&atilde;o exoplanetas?</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"351\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Exoplanetas s&atilde;o planetas que orbitam estrelas al&eacute;m do nosso Sol, pertencentes a outros sistemas. Foram detectados exoplanetas em milhares de sistemas estelares diferentes, mostrando a diversidade de mundos no universo.</span></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"275\" data-end=\"351\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><img src=\"https://www.brasilhilario.com.br/uploads/images/687fb5ba35aa8.jpg\" alt=\"imagem dos exoplanetas\" width=\"650\" height=\"468\"></span></p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"358\" data-end=\"402\">Quantidade confirmada (e em crescimento).</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"404\" data-end=\"646\">\r\n<li data-start=\"404\" data-end=\"484\">\r\n<p data-start=\"406\" data-end=\"484\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">No in&iacute;cio de 2022, a Nasa j&aacute; registrava mais de <strong data-start=\"48\" data-end=\"69\">5.000 exoplanetas</strong> confirmados.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"485\" data-end=\"565\">\r\n<p data-start=\"487\" data-end=\"565\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Em 2024, a cifra superou <strong data-start=\"25\" data-end=\"34\" data-is-last-node=\"\">5.600.</strong></span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"566\" data-end=\"646\">\r\n<p data-start=\"568\" data-end=\"646\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">E estudos mais recentes apontam o total atual em cerca de <strong data-start=\"58\" data-end=\"79\">7.510 exoplanetas</strong> catalogados.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"648\" data-end=\"687\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Ou seja, o n&uacute;mero cresce continuamente gra&ccedil;as aos avan&ccedil;os tecnol&oacute;gicos, como os telesc&oacute;pios Kepler, TESS, Hubble e James Webb.</span></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"648\" data-end=\"687\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"694\" data-end=\"733\">Como esses planetas s&atilde;o detectados?</h3>\r\n<p data-start=\"735\" data-end=\"776\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Os principais m&eacute;todos incluem:</span></p>\r\n<ul data-start=\"777\" data-end=\"1029\">\r\n<li data-start=\"777\" data-end=\"861\">\r\n<p data-start=\"779\" data-end=\"861\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"12\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Tr&acirc;nsito</strong>: ao passar na frente da estrela, o planeta reduz levemente seu brilho (~76% dos casos).</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"862\" data-end=\"946\">\r\n<p data-start=\"864\" data-end=\"946\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"38\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Velocidade radial (efeito Doppler)</strong>: mudan&ccedil;as no brilho da estrela indicam influ&ecirc;ncia gravitacional do planeta (~19%).</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"947\" data-end=\"1029\">\r\n<p data-start=\"949\" data-end=\"1029\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"23\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Lente gravitacional</strong> (~2%) e <strong data-start=\"32\" data-end=\"51\">imagens diretas</strong> (&lt;1%), usadas em situa&ccedil;&otilde;es espec&iacute;ficas.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1031\" data-end=\"1111\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Turbinas espaciais como o <strong data-start=\"26\" data-end=\"36\">Kepler</strong> (desde 2009) e o <strong data-start=\"54\" data-end=\"62\">TESS</strong> (desde 2018) t&ecirc;m sido cruciais nesse trabalho.</span></p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1031\" data-end=\"1111\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 data-start=\"1118\" data-end=\"1152\">Destaques entre os exoplanetas.</h3>\r\n<ul data-start=\"1154\" data-end=\"1406\">\r\n<li data-start=\"1154\" data-end=\"1238\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1156\" data-end=\"1238\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"27\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Draugr (PSR B1257+12 b)</strong>: exoplaneta extremamente leve, cerca de duas vezes a massa da Lua.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1154\" data-end=\"1238\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1156\" data-end=\"1238\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"15\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Kepler-186f</strong> e <strong data-start=\"18\" data-end=\"33\">Kepler-452b</strong>: super-Terras localizadas em zonas habit&aacute;veis, com potencial para &aacute;gua l&iacute;quida.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li data-start=\"1324\" data-end=\"1406\">\r\n<p data-start=\"1326\" data-end=\"1406\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\"><strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"19\" data-is-only-node=\"\">Super-J&uacute;piteres</strong>, <strong data-start=\"21\" data-end=\"42\">J&uacute;piteres quentes</strong> e protoplanetas como MWC 758 c tamb&eacute;m fazem parte das descobertas recentes.</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1521\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">A NASA planeja lan&ccedil;ar o <strong data-start=\"24\" data-end=\"65\">Telesc&oacute;pio Espacial Nancy Grace Roman</strong> (pr&eacute;-2027) e miss&otilde;es como <strong data-start=\"92\" data-end=\"101\">Ariel</strong> (ESA, 2029) para estudar atmosferas exoplanet&aacute;rias. Espera-se que novas descobertas incluam sinais vitais ou assinaturas de vida</span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p data-start=\"1441\" data-end=\"1521\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 data-start=\"1999\" data-end=\"2008\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\">Fontes</span></h2>\r\n<p data-start=\"2012\" data-end=\"2093\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Wikip&eacute;dia &ndash; <strong data-start=\"12\" data-end=\"26\">Exoplaneta</strong>: hist&oacute;rico e defini&ccedil;&atilde;o de exoplanetas</span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://pt.wikipedia.org/wiki/Exoplaneta?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Tek Not&iacute;cias</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+8</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Wikip&eacute;dia</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+8</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Brasil Escola</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+8</span></span></span></a><br></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">CNN Brasil &ndash; &copy;2022:&nbsp;<em data-start=\"20\" data-end=\"90\" data-is-last-node=\"\">&ldquo;Existem mais de 5.000 mundos al&eacute;m do nosso sistema solar, diz Nasa&rdquo;</em></span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.cnnbrasil.com.br/tecnologia/existem-mais-de-5-000-mundos-alem-do-nosso-sistema-solar-diz-nasa/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Tek Not&iacute;cias</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+2</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">CNN Brasil</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+2</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Gazeta do Povo</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+2</span></span></span></a><br></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">GAAIS/Unesp &ndash; Atualizado em 2025: <em data-start=\"34\" data-end=\"84\" data-is-last-node=\"\">&ldquo;J&aacute; foram confirmados mais de 5.600 exoplanetas&rdquo;</em></span> <span class=\"\" data-state=\"closed\"><span class=\"ms-1 inline-flex max-w-full items-center relative top-[-0.094rem] animate-[show_150ms_ease-in]\"><a class=\"flex h-4.5 overflow-hidden rounded-xl px-2 text-[9px] font-medium text-token-text-secondary! bg-[#F4F4F4]! dark:bg-[#303030]! transition-colors duration-150 ease-in-out\" href=\"https://www.feis.unesp.br/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span class=\"relative start-0 bottom-0 flex h-full w-full items-center\"><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Feis Unesp</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span><span class=\"flex h-4 w-full items-center justify-between absolute\"><span class=\"max-w-full grow truncate overflow-hidden text-center\">Tek Not&iacute;cias</span><span class=\"-me-1 flex h-full items-center rounded-full px-1 text-[#8F8F8F]\">+1</span></span></span></a><br></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span class=\"relative -mx-px my-[-0.2rem] rounded px-px py-[0.2rem] transition-colors duration-100 ease-in-out\">Facebook/Ci&ecirc;ncia em Foco &ndash; <em data-st